      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="sc161a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <salute>Sir</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>If <name>Mr. Stonefield</name> should agree for your two blacks, I will pay you the cash by the arrival of any moneys that come into my hands, which will not be many weeks <unclear> past</unclear>_</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>I am Sir Your <choice>
                     <abbr>Hum Servt</abbr>
                     <expan>Humble Servant</expan>
                  </choice>_</salute>
               <signed>
